<h2 class="styleguide__header">Link Handler</h1>

<h3>Popout links</h3>
<div class="span--3">
<p class="span--12">
Popout links open in a new window. 
</p>

<div class="span--12">
	<h4>Options</h4>
	<span class="code">data-name</span> 
	<p>Name of the new window</p>

	<span class="code">data-args</span> 
	<p>Arguments for window size, scroll bars, etc. <br/>
	<a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/open#Position_and_size_features" target="_blank">MDN Documentation</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="span--9">
	<div class="example-box example-box--vertical">
			<div class="example-box__code">
				<pre class="code">
&lt;a href=&quot;&lt;%= some_link_from_rails %&gt;&quot; data-component=&quot;popout&quot; data-args=&quot;height=600,width=800&quot;&gt;
My Link Name
&lt;/a&gt;
				</pre>
			</div>

			<div class="example-box__example">

				<a href="http://google.com/" data-component="popout-link" data-args="scrollbars=0,height=800,width=1024">Popout Link</a>

			</div>
		</div>
	<p>
</div>
